{"favorite_id": 10089, "calc_type": "", "dosing": false, "full_title_en": "HScore for Reactive Hemophagocytic Syndrome", "short_title_en": "HScore", "medium_description_en": "<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-5e66a879-7fff-dee3-17d2-41b1a7e6eabd\">Diagnoses reactive hemophagocytic syndrome. </span>", "short_description_en": "Hemophagocytic syndrome diagnosis.", "before_use": "<p>We launched a <a href=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/covid-19\" target=\"_blank\">COVID-19 Resource Center</a>, including a critical review of recommended calcs.</p>\n<p><strong>Tips for COVID-19:</strong> Screens for cytokine storm (<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(20)30628-0/fulltext\" target=\"_blank\">including in COVID-19</a>), when immunosuppression <em>may</em> be helpful (immunosuppression not yet shown to be beneficial).</p>", "instructions_en": "", "purpose_en": ["Diagnosis"], "disease_en": ["Cancer", "COVID-19", "Coronavirus"], "specialty_en": ["Hematology and Oncology"], "chief_complaint_en": ["Any/All"], "system_en": ["Hematologic", "Oncologic"], "search_abbreviation_en": ["HScore", "hemophagocytic syndrome score", "hemophagocytic risk", "hemophagocytic score", "h score", "h-score", "coronavirus", "covid", "covid-19", "covid 19", "covid19"], "slug": "hscore-reactive-hemophagocytic-syndrome", "seo": {"meta_description_en": "The HScore for Reactive Hemophagocytic Syndrome estimates the risk of having reactive hemophagocytic syndrome.", "keywords_en": "HScore, reactive hemophagocytic syndrome, Hemophagocytic Syndrome"}, "content": {"how_to_use": {"use_case_en": "<p>Do you use the HScore for Reactive Hemophagocytic Syndrome and want to contribute your expertise? <a href=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/join-us\" target=\"_blank\">Join</a> our contributor team!</p>", "pearls_pitfalls_en": "", "why_use_en": ""}, "next_steps": {"advice_en": "<p>Do you use the HScore for Reactive Hemophagocytic Syndrome and want to contribute your expertise?&nbsp;<a href=\"https:/